her past assistance.

20
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,610
Thus, she is specially granted

21
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,780
the title of Princess Huaisang,

22
00:02:01,910 --> 00:02:03,690
with jurisdiction over 500 households.

23
00:02:03,910 --> 00:02:05,910
The local government shall implement it.

24
00:02:05,910 --> 00:02:07,330
I've received the decree.

25
00:02:07,470 --> 00:02:08,780
Thank you.

26
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:13,870
Princess Huaisang, please rise.

27
00:02:13,870 --> 00:02:15,100
Everyone, please rise.

28
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,690
I have other urgent matters.

29
00:02:24,110 --> 00:02:24,950
I must take my leave.

30
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:33,950
Father.

31
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,270
I said that Miantang

32
00:02:35,270 --> 00:02:36,850
has contributed to the Emperor.

33
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:38,870
Now,

34
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:39,990
Miantang and the Lord

35
00:02:39,990 --> 00:02:41,750
are indeed a good match.

36
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,690
But the name "Huaisang"

37
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:49,620
with mourning sounds so ominous.

38
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,550
Well.

39
00:02:52,550 --> 00:02:54,850
What does "Huaisang" mean?

40
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,220
People often say

41
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,860
"sang" and "zi" represent homes.

42
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:01,020
I am Lord Huaiyang.

43
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:03,690
Miantang represents my home.

44
00:03:04,270 --> 00:03:06,010
If she's called "Huaizi",

45
00:03:06,390 --> 00:03:08,500
meaning childbirth,

46
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,140
it would be too hasty.

47
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:12,780
The name "Huaisang"

48
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,900
is just right.

49
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:16,080
Thank His Majesty for his consideration.

50
00:03:17,670 --> 00:03:18,730
He's done a great favor.

51
00:03:26,430 --> 00:03:28,730
Why did His Majesty suddenly grant me a title?

52
00:03:29,830 --> 00:03:30,730
Yes.

53
00:03:31,870 --> 00:03:33,190
Why was it given suddenly?

54
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,730
Please explain clearly.

55
00:03:35,670 --> 00:03:36,660
Well.

56
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,620
I guess

57
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,550
someone achieved military merit in Beizhou

58
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:41,900
and asked the Emperor for a reward.

59
00:03:43,550 --> 00:03:45,900
I am just a small local lord.

60
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,270
What right do I have

61
00:03:47,270 --> 00:03:49,130
to seek the title of Princess?

62
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,340
The Emperor is so petty.

63
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,250
I just asked for a jade,

64
00:03:56,670 --> 00:03:57,690
and he became anxious.

65
00:03:58,390 --> 00:03:59,690
So,

66
00:03:59,830 --> 00:04:01,590
you planned for the reward,

67
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:03,410
broken leg,

68
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:05,500
marriage certificate, and title?

69
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:11,100
I thought you were as hard as iron before.

70
00:04:11,390 --> 00:04:13,570
