71
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,850
If you want to call it a plot,

72
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,150
it's fate

73
00:04:19,150 --> 00:04:20,460
that aligns perfectly.

74
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:26,300
