88
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,780
all sorted?

89
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:03,020
Have you packed

90
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:04,650
all the items I prepared?

91
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,710
Grandfather.

92
00:05:08,710 --> 00:05:10,410
What? Forgotten?

93
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,320
