95
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:14,730
No, no, no.

96
00:05:15,150 --> 00:05:17,260
I had people check it three times.

97
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,820
Everything is ready.

98
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:27,700
