104
00:06:01,350 --> 00:06:03,340
I bid farewell to Grandfather.

105
00:06:03,710 --> 00:06:06,680
I wish Grandfather good health

106
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,100
and a long life.

107
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:09,930
May the Qiao family

108
00:06:10,350 --> 00:06:12,460
be safe and prosperous.

109
00:06:20,470 --> 00:06:21,340
Uncle,

110
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,340
