119
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:56,930
They've signed the marriage certificate?

120
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:58,630
Yes.

121
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:09,370
Your Majesty.

122
00:08:12,710 --> 00:08:14,140
In the end,

123
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,900
she still chose Lord Huaiyang.

124
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,410
According to the customs,

125
00:08:26,030 --> 00:08:27,240
the marriage of a lord

126
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,140
requires approval from me.

127
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:09,490
My Lord,

128
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:11,680
let me and the shadow guards

129
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:13,060
escort you and Madam.

130
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:16,870
