203
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:03,250
compare to the previous one?

204
00:14:05,350 --> 00:14:06,190
Mrs...

205
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:07,630
Mrs. Cui.

206
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:08,470
Ladies,

207
00:14:08,470 --> 00:14:10,010
