213
00:14:42,230 --> 00:14:43,070
Madam.

214
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:45,970
I knew it.

215
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:48,820
The bond between us isn't over.

216
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:52,340
In the past,

217
00:14:53,110 --> 00:14:54,580
