228
00:15:19,990 --> 00:15:22,040
Madam, are you hungry?

229
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:23,870
I'll cook for you right away.

230
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:25,870
Come on, Bicao. Come on.

231
00:15:25,870 --> 00:15:27,560
You go prepare as well.

232
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,400
Hurry up.

233
00:15:28,630 --> 00:15:29,470
Quickly.

234
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:30,700
Why does no one

235
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,200
care about me?

236
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:34,470
You've learned to eavesdrop now.

237
00:15:34,470 --> 00:15:35,960
Once the vixen next door comes back,

238
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,110
you lose your manners, huh?

239
00:15:37,110 --> 00:15:38,390
- Come down here.
- Dear, dear.

240
00:15:38,390 --> 00:15:39,730
- I'm coming.
- The courtyard

241
00:15:40,010 --> 00:15:41,460
- is as usual.
- You didn't tell me.

242
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:42,610
As usual.

243
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:45,460
The new year is better than the old.

244
00:15:46,710 --> 00:15:48,320
With their hair bound,

245
