248
00:15:55,830 --> 00:15:57,160
It's also to fulfill

249
00:15:57,160 --> 00:15:59,370
the affection I have with Xingzhou.

250
00:16:00,110 --> 00:16:01,700
You silly child.

251
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:04,340
How could I bear it?

252
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:09,700
What's wrong with you?

253
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:12,800
I see you two are like

254
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:14,770
mother and daughter.

255
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,010
But from today on,

256
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:19,890
