258
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:24,350
I watched Binglan grow up.

259
00:16:24,350 --> 00:16:26,400
Even if she can't marry Xingzhou,

260
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:27,890
I still care for her.

261
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,850
Can't marry him?

262
00:16:32,110 --> 00:16:33,460
Back then,

263
00:16:33,990 --> 00:16:35,770
when Binglan was bedridden,

264
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:38,830
Xingzhou seized the chance
to break off the engagement.

265
00:16:38,830 --> 00:16:39,920
I know

266
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:42,250
you feel guilty about it.

267
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:45,160
I'm worried you will try to make up for it

268
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:47,490
by making Binglan a princess.

269
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:49,820
That's quite inappropriate.

270
00:16:53,110 --> 00:16:55,130
Mother is confused with worry.

271
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:56,830
She's afraid that the Princess,

272
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:58,130
with her wealth and pride,

273
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:00,940
might make it hard for me

274
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:03,100
in Zhenzhou

275
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:05,340
because of my past with Xingzhou.

276
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:07,500
Don't worry.

277
00:17:09,070 --> 00:17:10,200
Now,

278
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,230
Xingzhou is no longer

279
00:17:11,230 --> 00:17:13,230
with those charming women

280
00:17:13,230 --> 00:17:14,610
from Lingquan Town.

281
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:16,370
Princess Huaisang.

282
00:17:16,840 --> 00:17:19,100
