283
00:17:19,620 --> 00:17:21,020
she is most likely

284
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:23,380
a newly esteemed lady with merit.

285
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:25,700
She's from a well-mannered family.

286
00:17:25,820 --> 00:17:27,620
She won't make things difficult for you.

287
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:35,860
Sister,

288
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:37,980
why don't you

289
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:40,100
