291
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:45,540
Why would she give up her position

292
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:46,580
as a main wife

293
00:17:46,580 --> 00:17:47,500
to become a concubine?

294
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:49,580
No, no. That's not what I meant.

295
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:51,100
What I meant was

296
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:53,420
if the Princess is reasonable,

297
00:17:53,820 --> 00:17:56,140
you should raise Binglan to be the main wife.

298
00:17:56,260 --> 00:17:58,300
She won't refuse.

299
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:00,420
Well.

300
00:18:00,420 --> 00:18:01,340
Aunt,

301
00:18:01,940 --> 00:18:04,820
everyone knows I'm with Xingzhou here.

302
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:07,020
Besides him,

303
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:10,220
who else could I marry?

304
00:18:10,820 --> 00:18:11,700
Then...

305
00:18:11,900 --> 00:18:12,740
Consort Dowager,

306
00:18:13,180 --> 00:18:14,500
the Lord's letter.

307
00:18:15,940 --> 00:18:17,460
Xingzhou's letter has arrived.

308
00:18:17,460 --> 00:18:19,660
Look, here it comes.

309
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:20,620
Mother.

310
00:18:20,620 --> 00:18:21,980
We should go.

311
00:18:22,260 --> 00:18:23,140
It's fine.

312
00:18:23,140 --> 00:18:24,460
We're all family.

313
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:26,220
Manager Gao, read it.

314
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:27,060
Yes.

315
00:18:33,900 --> 00:18:35,460
Mother, are you alright?

316
00:18:36,020 --> 00:18:36,900
Manager Gao.

317
00:18:37,260 --> 00:18:39,940
I know you're reading the letter for Mother.

318
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:42,700
You and the other people should leave.

319
00:18:42,820 --> 00:18:45,260
Mother will read it alone.

320
00:18:51,780 --> 00:18:53,020
What are you waiting for?

321
00:18:53,020 --> 00:18:53,860
Go now.

322
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:54,700
Yes.

323
00:18:56,980 --> 00:18:58,340
You all leave too.

324
00:18:58,820 --> 00:18:59,660
Sister.

325
00:18:59,740 --> 00:19:01,220
We're family.

326
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:02,060
Mother.

327
00:19:15,900 --> 00:19:17,660
The Princess and I have arrived in Zhenzhou.

328
00:19:17,860 --> 00:19:19,420
This is to inform you of our safety

329
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:21,580
and to ease your worries.

330
00:19:21,740 --> 00:19:23,420
To explain about the Princess:

331
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:25,100
Her name is Liu Miantang.

332
00:19:25,260 --> 00:19:26,740
Her ancestral home is Beizhou County.

333
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,580
Other people?

334
00:19:30,740 --> 00:19:31,820
What's the matter?

335
00:19:31,820 --> 00:19:33,220
Marrying the Princess,

336
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:34,420
he's forgotten all the folks

337
00:19:34,420 --> 00:19:35,500
in Zhenzhou.

338
00:19:36,420 --> 00:19:37,620
- Mother.
- Mrs. Lian.

339
00:19:42,460 --> 00:19:43,460
Mrs. Lian.

340
00:19:44,300 --> 00:19:45,820
Actually, I read

341
00:19:45,900 --> 00:19:47,500
that letter a bit more.

342
00:19:48,140 --> 00:19:49,420
What did the Lord say?

343
00:19:49,420 --> 00:19:51,700
He said he was staying in Lingquan Town

344
00:19:51,820 --> 00:19:52,980
to announce the marriage

345
00:19:52,980 --> 00:19:54,300
to the people of Zhenzhou

346
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:55,420
before he came back.

347
00:19:55,660 --> 00:19:56,980
He won't return yet.

348
00:19:58,620 --> 00:19:59,820
And...

349
00:20:00,340 --> 00:20:01,660
And?

350
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:04,420
Miantang offered strategies for the Xizhou war.

351
00:20:04,820 --> 00:20:06,500
The Emperor, impressed by her hard work,

352
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:09,060
bestowed her the title of Princess Huaisang.

353
00:20:09,420 --> 00:20:10,900
I'm increasingly devoted to her.

354
00:20:10,900 --> 00:20:12,620
I love and respect her.

355
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:15,140
In this life, I will only marry her.

356
00:20:15,460 --> 00:20:19,420
With her in this life is enough.

357
00:20:23,500 --> 00:20:24,660
Thank you, Mrs. Lian.

358
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:33,550
If that mistress marries him,

359
00:20:33,550 --> 00:20:35,580
she won't allow you in the mansion.

360
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:38,340
Let alone being a main wife.

361
00:20:41,940 --> 00:20:43,460
To identify a mistress?

362
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:45,100
You three need

363
00:20:45,260 --> 00:20:46,980
to claim to be neighbors from North Street.

364
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:48,460
In front of those noble families,

365
00:20:48,780 --> 00:20:50,700
identify Ms. Liu
from Yushao Porcelain Shop

366
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:51,940
and tell them she's been kept

367
00:20:52,300 --> 00:20:54,220
by the Lord in Lingquan Town for a year.

368
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:55,340
This...

369
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,500
Are you really going to sleep there?

370
00:21:08,570 --> 00:21:10,020
Without the proper ceremony,

371
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:11,500
sharing a bed

372
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:13,020
is too much.

373
00:21:14,250 --> 00:21:16,180
I don't know Lord Huaiyang.

374
00:21:16,180 --> 00:21:17,780
I didn't expect him to be a man

375
00:21:17,780 --> 00:21:19,180
of propriety and rules.

376
00:21:19,930 --> 00:21:21,140
May I ask

377
00:21:21,140 --> 00:21:23,940
what kind of person Cui Jiu was

378
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:25,140
who once shared my bed?

379
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:27,140
Yes.

380
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:28,300
Who is he?

381
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,660
How can you think of him like that?

382
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:31,700
Let's sleep.

383
00:21:48,900 --> 00:21:50,700
Aren't you going to sleep there?

384
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:52,100
I've changed my mind.

385
00:21:53,300 --> 00:21:54,260
Rogue.

386
00:21:54,620 --> 00:21:55,540
Who's the rogue?

387
00:21:57,260 --> 00:21:59,020
First, you mocked me.

388
00:21:59,020 --> 00:22:00,540
Then, you left me hanging.

389
00:22:00,540 --> 00:22:01,580
You're the rogue.

390
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:05,820
Without proper ceremony,

391
00:22:05,820 --> 00:22:06,940
you overstepped.

392
00:22:08,860 --> 00:22:09,700
Fine.

393
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:10,660
Let's sleep.

394
00:22:22,140 --> 00:22:22,980
Your kiss back.

395
00:22:23,260 --> 00:22:24,100
We're even now.

396
00:22:29,820 --> 00:22:31,660
I want to hold another village banquet.

397
00:22:35,180 --> 00:22:36,660
To catch thieves again?

398
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:40,020
Is that my only strategy?

399
00:22:40,340 --> 00:22:42,220
If I set up a feast every time there's a thief,

400
00:22:42,220 --> 00:22:43,700
all the people in Zhenzhou

401
00:22:43,700 --> 00:22:45,140
will become outlaws.

402
00:22:46,180 --> 00:22:47,780
Then why have a village banquet?

403
00:22:47,900 --> 00:22:49,140
I feel that we

404
00:22:49,140 --> 00:22:50,540
have been through so much,

405
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:52,700
going around in circles,

406
00:22:52,700 --> 00:22:53,620
and ending up here.

407
00:22:54,580 --> 00:22:56,220
I want to make up for past regrets.

408
00:22:56,460 --> 00:22:58,300
Let you present yourself properly

409
00:22:58,300 --> 00:22:59,580
to start afresh.

410
00:23:03,100 --> 00:23:05,060
I think I've said this before.

411
00:23:05,060 --> 00:23:05,900
But

412
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:07,060
this time,

413
00:23:07,420 --> 00:23:08,260
I'm serious.

414
00:23:11,300 --> 00:23:12,140
I trust you.

415
00:23:43,420 --> 00:23:44,460
Fellow villagers.

416
00:23:45,140 --> 00:23:46,460
Fellow villagers.

417
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:47,300
Alright.

418
00:23:47,420 --> 00:23:49,140
Everyone, quiet down.

419
00:23:49,140 --> 00:23:50,770
Let me say a few words.

420
00:23:51,940 --> 00:23:53,620
I've been troubling everyone

421
00:23:53,620 --> 00:23:54,740
in Lingquan Town

422
00:23:55,030 --> 00:23:56,220
for a while now.

423
00:23:56,500 --> 00:23:58,060
I've caused you all some trouble.

424
00:23:58,060 --> 00:24:00,820
Today, enjoy your food and drink.

425
00:24:00,820 --> 00:24:02,380
I'll start with a drink.

426
00:24:02,620 --> 00:24:04,580
Good, good, good.

427
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:05,820
Great!

428
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:07,380
But,

429
00:24:07,380 --> 00:24:08,220
villagers,

430
00:24:08,460 --> 00:24:09,300
is one drink enough?

431
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:11,660
At least ten drinks.

432
00:24:11,660 --> 00:24:13,340
- Right?
- Right.

433
00:24:13,340 --> 00:24:14,460
Ten drinks.

434
00:24:14,820 --> 00:24:15,820
Ten drinks.

435
00:24:18,820 --> 00:24:19,700
Come on.

436
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:20,900
Eat up.

437
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:22,500
Madam,

438
00:24:23,020 --> 00:24:24,380
look at the master.

439
00:24:24,500 --> 00:24:25,660
He's never been like this.

440
00:24:25,660 --> 00:24:27,100
Aren't you going to do something?

441
00:24:27,620 --> 00:24:29,180
He's always been so reserved.

442
00:24:29,180 --> 00:24:30,300
I'm actually glad to see him

443
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:31,460
let loose for once.

444
00:24:32,180 --> 00:24:33,260
Mr. Cui,

445
00:24:33,380 --> 00:24:35,660
no wonder you've made a name
for yourself in the army.

446
00:24:35,660 --> 00:24:37,100
You're truly impressive.

447
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:37,940
Yes.

448
00:24:38,100 --> 00:24:39,980
We were blind before.

449
00:24:39,980 --> 00:24:40,860
You know?

450
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:41,820
Ms. Liu

451
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:43,860
is a true heroine.

452
00:24:43,860 --> 00:24:45,780
How could she marry a dandy?

453
00:24:45,780 --> 00:24:47,060
Yes, yes, yes.

454
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:48,660
- Come on.
- Fellow villagers.

455
00:24:49,180 --> 00:24:50,180
I'd like

456
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:52,340
to propose another toast.

457
00:24:52,660 --> 00:24:53,700
Actually,

458
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:56,860
I am...

459
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:05,260
You are actually

460
00:25:05,260 --> 00:25:07,140
quite afraid

461
00:25:08,100 --> 00:25:10,780
of your wife.

462
00:25:15,820 --> 00:25:16,980
She always

463
00:25:17,860 --> 00:25:21,540
had him under control.

464
00:25:22,540 --> 00:25:23,820
He'd been holding back

465
00:25:23,980 --> 00:25:25,220
his frustration,

466
00:25:25,220 --> 00:25:28,380
which is why he joined the army.

467
00:25:30,780 --> 00:25:31,660
I

468
00:25:31,660 --> 00:25:33,780
live next door to him.

469
00:25:34,380 --> 00:25:35,980
I hear

470
00:25:36,780 --> 00:25:37,660
their arguments

471
00:25:38,140 --> 00:25:40,540
clearly.

472
00:25:40,540 --> 00:25:42,500
Honey, you're drunk.

473
00:25:42,500 --> 00:25:44,140
Sorry, everyone.

474
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:45,380
Too much to drink.

475
00:25:45,380 --> 00:25:46,580
Sorry, sorry.

476
00:25:48,260 --> 00:25:49,140
Cui!

477
00:25:50,340 --> 00:25:53,380
Even if you run to the ends of the earth,

478
00:25:53,500 --> 00:25:55,700
you'll still be kicked back

479
00:25:55,700 --> 00:25:57,460
by your tiger at home.

480
00:26:00,420 --> 00:26:01,460
Zhang.

481
00:26:02,820 --> 00:26:04,580
He's wrong.

482
00:26:05,460 --> 00:26:09,140
My wife is gentle and virtuous.

483
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:10,980
If there's someone to blame,

484
00:26:11,100 --> 00:26:12,020
it is

485
00:26:12,180 --> 00:26:13,140
my fault.

486
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:24,020
I'm Wen Shisan from Zhenzhou Army Camp.

487
00:26:24,020 --> 00:26:26,220
Greetings, My Lord.

488
00:26:30,300 --> 00:26:31,300
Come on.

489
00:26:31,860 --> 00:26:33,860
Get up, get up, get up.

490
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:36,100
You...

491
00:26:38,540 --> 00:26:40,060
What are you talking about?

492
00:26:40,620 --> 00:26:43,580
You must be drunk.

493
00:26:45,220 --> 00:26:47,540
There's no lord here.

494
00:26:47,540 --> 00:26:48,460
Yes.

495
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:49,580
Who's the Lord here?

496
00:26:49,580 --> 00:26:51,180
I'm Aide Huang.

497
00:26:51,180 --> 00:26:52,660
A squad leader under my command

498
00:26:53,180 --> 00:26:54,220
once had the honor

499
00:26:54,220 --> 00:26:55,900
of meeting the Lord in battle.

500
00:26:56,780 --> 00:26:57,620
This

501
00:26:57,660 --> 00:26:58,740
is Lord Huaiyang.

502
00:27:00,260 --> 00:27:01,100
Lord Huaiyang.

503
00:27:01,940 --> 00:27:02,980
Lord Huaiyang.

504
00:27:03,660 --> 00:27:05,100
The Lord led from the front,

505
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:06,660
risking his life with us.

506
00:27:06,940 --> 00:27:08,500
We would never mistake him.

507
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:09,900
Lord Huaiyang.

508
00:27:09,900 --> 00:27:11,060
You've caused trouble.

509
00:27:11,060 --> 00:27:12,300
Quickly, kneel!

510
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:15,460
Forgive me, My Lord. Forgive me.

511
00:27:15,460 --> 00:27:16,940
Come on. Get up. Get up.

512
00:27:17,140 --> 00:27:17,980
Get up.

513
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:19,100
It's alright.

514
00:27:19,700 --> 00:27:20,660
I am

515
00:27:20,980 --> 00:27:22,700
indeed Lord Huaiyang.

516
00:27:23,460 --> 00:27:24,900
It's truly Lord Huaiyang.

517
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:28,540
Greetings, My Lord.

518
00:27:28,540 --> 00:27:30,060
Everyone, no need for formalities.

519
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:32,380
No formalities, no formalities.

520
00:27:33,250 --> 00:27:34,540
Disguised as a merchant,

521
00:27:34,950 --> 00:27:36,620
I've been staying in Lingquan Town.

522
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:38,060
I had

523
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:39,820
official duties.

524
00:27:40,020 --> 00:27:41,260
I had no choice but to do so.

525
00:27:41,670 --> 00:27:42,700
The matter is resolved.

526
00:27:42,860 --> 00:27:44,380
I wanted to take this opportunity

527
00:27:44,540 --> 00:27:46,660
to reveal the truth to everyone.

528
00:27:47,740 --> 00:27:49,380
I have

529
00:27:49,820 --> 00:27:51,740
troubled all of you.

530
00:27:52,420 --> 00:27:54,620
No, no, no.

531
00:27:55,500 --> 00:27:57,020
I just want to apologize

532
00:27:57,140 --> 00:27:59,220
to everyone here.

533
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:00,300
Sorry.

534
00:28:02,100 --> 00:28:03,100
This is unacceptable.

535
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:04,260
We can't accept that.

536
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:09,660
You're a lord.

537
00:28:09,900 --> 00:28:12,660
Then Mrs. Cui must be...

538
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:15,580
She's the future Princess of Huaiyang.

539
00:28:17,300 --> 00:28:18,900
Greetings, My Lady.

540
00:28:19,380 --> 00:28:20,580
No need for formalities.

541
00:28:21,580 --> 00:28:23,100
My wife and I have received care

542
00:28:23,100 --> 00:28:24,820
from everyone for a long time.

543
00:28:24,820 --> 00:28:26,780
We are truly grateful.

544
00:28:28,620 --> 00:28:30,060
It should be us thanking you.

545
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,780
Calling me your wife now?

546
00:28:34,260 --> 00:28:35,580
Everyone, don't be too polite.

547
00:28:35,580 --> 00:28:37,540
Raise your glasses.

548
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:43,940
Today,

549
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:46,700
please drink

550
00:28:47,540 --> 00:28:49,060
with us.

551
00:28:49,060 --> 00:28:50,340
Enjoy the feast.

552
00:28:51,380 --> 00:28:52,220
Alright.

553
00:28:52,780 --> 00:28:56,340
I'd like to drink this toast with you both.

554
00:28:56,980 --> 00:28:58,140
Wishing the Lord

555
00:28:58,700 --> 00:28:59,940
and the Princess

556
00:28:59,940 --> 00:29:02,300
years of flourishing flowers

557
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:05,780
and family reunions year after year.

558
00:29:06,900 --> 00:29:07,980
Well said!

559
00:29:07,980 --> 00:29:09,500
Good! Good!

560
00:29:09,500 --> 00:29:11,220
To the Lord and the Princess.

561
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:12,340
Let's drink together.

562
00:29:12,500 --> 00:29:13,340
Come on.

563
00:29:13,740 --> 00:29:15,660
Let's drink.

564
00:29:17,300 --> 00:29:18,980
I didn't know before

565
00:29:18,980 --> 00:29:20,500
that you enjoy lively occasions

566
00:29:20,780 --> 00:29:22,180
and can drink so well.

567
00:29:25,300 --> 00:29:26,260
Housewarming

568
00:29:26,260 --> 00:29:28,140
is to congratulate on the new home.

569
00:29:28,380 --> 00:29:29,660
This isn't the Lord's mansion.

570
00:29:30,020 --> 00:29:31,260
Where's your home?

571
00:29:33,860 --> 00:29:35,220
A place of the heart.

572
00:29:36,860 --> 00:29:37,740
Xingzhou,

573
00:29:38,260 --> 00:29:39,100
you've changed.

574
00:29:40,540 --> 00:29:42,140
You've become more amicable.

575
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:47,900
It seems Mother has read the letter.

576
00:29:48,980 --> 00:29:49,900
She agreed.

577
00:29:50,100 --> 00:29:51,220
If not,

578
00:29:51,220 --> 00:29:53,220
would I come here for a drink?

579
00:29:54,020 --> 00:29:55,700
You are Mother's only legitimate son.

580
00:29:55,980 --> 00:29:57,700
In the end, she values you.

581
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:58,820
Tomorrow,

582
00:29:58,980 --> 00:30:01,060
bring Princess Huaisang into the mansion.

583
00:30:12,380 --> 00:30:13,860
Such days

584
00:30:14,180 --> 00:30:15,860
won't come again, right?

585
00:30:17,420 --> 00:30:20,140
In the future, neighbors will avoid me.

586
00:30:21,060 --> 00:30:22,260
It will be quiet.

