00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:53,780
I never noticed you were

588
00:30:53,780 --> 00:30:54,940
so childish before.

589
00:30:55,380 --> 00:30:56,660
Let me tell you a secret.

590
00:30:56,860 --> 00:30:57,740
What secret?

591
00:30:58,580 --> 00:30:59,900
I'm afraid of the dark.

592
00:31:00,740 --> 00:31:02,180
You're afraid of the dark?

593
00:31:05,540 --> 00:31:07,140
When I was young, walking at night,

594
00:31:07,140 --> 00:31:09,900
I always needed Uncle to follow me.

595
00:31:10,460 --> 00:31:12,460
One time, Uncle scared me

596
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:13,420
and quietly left.

597
00:31:13,780 --> 00:31:15,260
I turned around and no one was there.

598
00:31:15,780 --> 00:31:17,260
I cried all night.

599
00:31:18,180 --> 00:31:19,700
Later, in Mount Yang,

600
00:31:20,300 --> 00:31:21,660
the nights there

601
00:31:21,900 --> 00:31:24,380
were darker than anywhere I'd seen.

602
00:31:25,260 --> 00:31:27,380
But I always had to walk at the back,

603
00:31:28,110 --> 00:31:30,460
because I became a reliable person for others.

604
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:38,660
How long since we came back

605
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:39,860
from the banquet?

606
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:41,660
How could you cheat on me?

607
00:31:41,670 --> 00:31:42,590
Nonsense.

608
00:31:42,730 --> 00:31:44,130
That's just a mason repairing walls.

609
00:31:44,140 --> 00:31:45,400
Repairing walls?

610
00:31:46,460 --> 00:31:48,260
What wall fell that needed repair in the dark?

611
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:50,620
Is it the wall in my backyard?

612
00:31:50,620 --> 00:31:51,940
It's the wall in the backyard.

613
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:53,820
Look at the Cui family next door.

614
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:55,420
Their wall was patched by the man.

615
00:31:55,430 --> 00:31:57,100
- Praising me.
- And he's the Lord.

616
00:31:57,100 --> 00:31:57,940
Unlike you,

617
00:31:58,100 --> 00:31:59,180
staying at home every day.

618
00:31:59,180 --> 00:32:00,420
