619
00:32:00,420 --> 00:32:01,260
Yes, yes, yes.

620
00:32:01,580 --> 00:32:02,860
Of course, he can do everything.

621
00:32:03,220 --> 00:32:04,420
He's the Lord.

622
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:06,380
Yes, he's the Lord.

623
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:08,540
You must be scared out of your wits.

624
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:12,220
It's so late.

625
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:13,580
Are you going to let anyone rest?

626
00:32:14,740 --> 00:32:16,700
Whose handkerchief is behind the wall?

627
00:32:16,700 --> 00:32:17,940
Aren't you afraid of losing it?

628
00:32:19,100 --> 00:32:20,180
Let's go check it out.

629
00:32:23,220 --> 00:32:24,060
Who is it?

630
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:42,340
Who is it?

631
00:32:42,940 --> 00:32:43,980
Isn't it your handkerchief?

632
00:32:43,980 --> 00:32:44,820
No, no, no.

633
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:46,180
This isn't mine.

634
00:32:46,660 --> 00:32:47,820
Where is your handkerchief?

635
00:32:49,460 --> 00:32:50,420
Still denying it?

636
00:32:51,180 --> 00:32:52,300
Did you climb the wall

637
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:53,780
to secretly meet that woman?

638
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:55,980
Explain yourself clearly.

639
00:32:56,220 --> 00:32:57,500
Come with me. Let's go.

640
00:32:59,260 --> 00:33:00,660
