00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:24,540
also benefit from it.

692
00:35:24,660 --> 00:35:25,900
Yes, yes.

693
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:28,380
The Lord and the Princess are a perfect match.

694
00:35:28,640 --> 00:35:30,730
