Indeed.

696
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:35,780
A pheasant thinks it's a phoenix

697
00:35:36,140 --> 00:35:38,010
just because of a feather.

698
00:35:50,780 --> 00:35:52,020
Once you pass this door,

699
00:35:52,020 --> 00:35:54,300
there's no room for regret or fear.

700
00:35:54,660 --> 00:35:55,700
Who is afraid?

701
00:35:56,060 --> 00:35:56,900
Princess,

702
00:35:57,260 --> 00:35:58,100
please.

703
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:03,340
The Lord has arrived.

704
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:16,020
Greetings, Mother.

705
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:18,620
