706
00:36:19,820 --> 00:36:22,540
I'm Liu Miantang. Greetings, Consort Dowager.

707
00:36:22,660 --> 00:36:24,180
Greetings, elders.

708
00:36:33,180 --> 00:36:34,500
Sorry to have worried you, Mother.

709
00:36:34,780 --> 00:36:36,100
I'm doing well.

710
00:36:40,780 --> 00:36:42,420
Not just well.

711
00:36:42,420 --> 00:36:44,620
Xingzhou is now in the limelight.

712
00:36:44,620 --> 00:36:45,940
As an aunt,

713
00:36:45,940 --> 00:36:47,940
I feel honored.

714
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:50,380
Yes, our family could rise

715
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:52,180
largely thanks to my nephew Xingzhou.

716
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:54,620
