717
00:36:55,950 --> 00:36:57,300
for the guest from the capital.

718
00:36:58,580 --> 00:37:00,140
You haven't married,

719
00:37:00,140 --> 00:37:01,500
yet you kept your mother waiting.

720
00:37:01,620 --> 00:37:02,620
Princess, serve tea

721
00:37:02,860 --> 00:37:04,060
to the Consort Dowager

722
00:37:04,060 --> 00:37:05,620
