725
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:12,820
I'm a junior.

726
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:13,740
It's not troublesome

727
00:37:13,740 --> 00:37:14,900
to serve tea to elders.

728
00:37:37,380 --> 00:37:38,780
Consort Dowager, have some tea.

729
00:37:44,460 --> 00:37:45,980
Princess, what do you mean?

730
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:49,980
Mother, are you alright?

731
00:37:53,220 --> 00:37:54,420
Princess,

732
00:37:54,700 --> 00:37:55,740
