734
00:37:57,900 --> 00:37:59,700
She probably can't even lift her chopsticks.

735
00:38:00,060 --> 00:38:01,700
It's not that serious.

736
00:38:02,180 --> 00:38:03,620
I was careless.

737
00:38:03,620 --> 00:38:04,980
Consort Dowager, please rest.

738
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:06,500
Let me serve you the dishes.

739
00:38:15,140 --> 00:38:16,740
Consort Dowager, please enjoy.

740
00:38:17,240 --> 00:38:18,380
Everyone, please take a seat.

741
00:38:18,540 --> 00:38:19,380
I'm fine standing.

742
00:38:21,060 --> 00:38:22,460
What do you mean by that?

743
00:38:22,660 --> 00:38:24,060
If this gets out,

744
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:26,180
people will think I'm bullying you.

745
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:27,300
How are you bullying her?

746
00:38:27,860 --> 00:38:29,140
You haven't hit or scolded her.

747
00:38:29,140 --> 00:38:30,420
How is this bullying?

748
00:38:30,940 --> 00:38:33,260
Would you guys say that my mother

749
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:34,500
is bullying her daughter-in-law?

750
00:38:38,260 --> 00:38:39,620
That's not what I meant.

751
00:38:39,620 --> 00:38:40,460
Mother, Mother.

752
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:41,740
I understand.

753
00:38:42,380 --> 00:38:43,540
Miantang knows too.

754
00:38:43,820 --> 00:38:45,100
She is filial

755
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:47,140
and worries about your hand.

756
00:38:47,420 --> 00:38:48,260
Miantang,

757
00:38:48,620 --> 00:38:50,220
you don't know

758
00:38:50,220 --> 00:38:51,500
how much my mother suffered

759
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:52,660
