and evening greetings every day,

762
00:38:56,620 --> 00:38:58,260
not daring to show any disobedience.

763
00:38:58,340 --> 00:39:00,140
I've always heard the Lord talk

764
00:39:00,140 --> 00:39:01,740
about your hardships.

765
00:39:02,980 --> 00:39:04,460
As the saying goes,

766
00:39:04,940 --> 00:39:06,860
hardships make a mother-in-law

767
00:39:06,860 --> 00:39:08,290
who can enjoy peace.

768
00:39:09,420 --> 00:39:10,620
Now my mother

769
00:39:10,780 --> 00:39:12,860
has become a mother-in-law.

770
00:39:14,260 --> 00:39:15,460
Relatives, bear witness.

771
00:39:15,620 --> 00:39:17,070
I swear here

772
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:18,940
that I will not side

773
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:20,060
with my wife in the future.

774
00:39:20,060 --> 00:39:21,460
I won't let my mother

775
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:23,140
suffer unjustly.

776
00:39:24,300 --> 00:39:25,420
If I break this oath,

777
00:39:26,780 --> 00:39:27,740
I'll ask for punishment.

778
00:39:28,170 --> 00:39:29,820
I will follow your example

779
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:32,660
and respect you with morning
and evening greetings.

780
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:35,420
Mother,

781
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:37,300
I've found a good

782
00:39:37,300 --> 00:39:38,700
daughter-in-law for you.

783
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:39,780
Even before marriage,

784
00:39:40,060 --> 00:39:41,700
she already regards you as a model.

785
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:50,620
