825
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:24,700
Can't you see we're dining?

826
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,180
We won't see them.

827
00:41:27,420 --> 00:41:29,260
Aunt, you should meet them.

828
00:41:29,860 --> 00:41:31,260
The Princess is new to Zhenzhou

829
00:41:31,260 --> 00:41:32,540
