830
00:41:32,540 --> 00:41:34,100
It's a blessing for our family.

831
00:41:34,450 --> 00:41:36,420
If there's something urgent,

832
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:37,740
Xingzhou

833
00:41:37,860 --> 00:41:39,500
